    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (n, coordinates) = case
        x = [coord[0] for coord in coordinates]
        y = [coord[1] for coord in coordinates]
        x.sort()
        y.sort()
        x1 = x[n // 2] - x[(n - 1) // 2] - 1
        y1 = y[n // 2] - y[(n - 1) // 2] + 1
        results.append(x1 * y1)
    return results
